    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139570/extras/1fa8bbcc413459268adfed26af884325.avif?t=1766070019\" width=616 height=75 /></span><br><strong>《Co-Op Kaiju Horror Cooking》</strong>，“合作开菊兽恐怖烹饪”，这个名字就是这款游戏的真实写照。你和你的朋友们是中世纪修道士、大厨——也是行走的灾难源。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139570/extras/e8d8d9dcaff2a11630fd0639af0dbdc9.poster.avif?t=1766070019\" aria-label=\"Gif of monks running down stairs and then all crowded around a sheet of paper\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139570/extras/e8d8d9dcaff2a11630fd0639af0dbdc9.webm?t=1766070019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139570/extras/e8d8d9dcaff2a11630fd0639af0dbdc9.mp4?t=1766070019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在这款极致荒诞的多人线上恐怖游戏中，2到4位你最青睐的伙伴（也可以更多，如果你不怕烧坏电脑或人脑的话）必须利用包括陷阱、近距离语音聊天、格里高利圣咏在内的工具，投喂被称为“开菊兽”(Kaiju)的巨型怪物、搜集宝藏，并阻止世界末日的发生。<br><br>你只有10分钟时间。<br>不要待在食物储藏室里。<br>别被逮到。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139570/extras/018c620d0634f3b1735dcf6c13f1c00e.poster.avif?t=1766070019\" aria-label=\"Gif showing monks running around a huge room filled with stairs and columns\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139570/extras/018c620d0634f3b1735dcf6c13f1c00e.webm?t=1766070019\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139570/extras/018c620d0634f3b1735dcf6c13f1c00e.mp4?t=1766070019\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>灵活的“标签式烹饪系统”。切碎食材、加盐、烧熟——然后把它们射进开菊兽的巨口之中！<br></li><li>一个关于与信仰搏斗的故事，在此期间你的领导们开始领盒饭，只剩下你来传递火炬，并一路坚持13关。<br></li><li>来自《Clickolding》和《I Am Your Beast》开发者的首款多人游戏。<br></li><li>大开大合的中世纪风配乐，出自屡获殊荣的作曲家David Mason之手（《Dredge》、《Creepy Redneck Dinosaur Mansion 3》。<br></li><li>逃离可怕怪物的魔爪——如果万不得已，也可以把它们变成食材。<br></li><li>没有番茄，毕竟番茄直到16世纪才传入欧洲。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3139570/extras/4e6740f694d6e422e07e45caacf1cbc5.avif?t=1766070019\" width=616 height=75 /></span>",
